@startuml Meal_Planning
title Use Case Diagram: Meal Planning (UC6)

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white

left to right direction

actor "User" as User #4ECDC4

rectangle "Meal Planning System" {
  package "Meal Plan Management" {
    usecase "UCS06-1\nCreate Meal Plan" as UC1 #FFE4B5
    usecase "UCS06-2\nView Meal Plan" as UC2 #E0F0FF
    usecase "UCS06-3\nUpdate Meal Plan" as UC3 #FFE4B5
    usecase "UCS06-4\nDelete Meal Plan" as UC4 #E0F0FF
  }
  
  package "Shopping List" {
    usecase "UCS06-5\nGenerate Shopping List" as UC5 #FFE4B5
  }
}

User --> UC1
User --> UC2
User --> UC3
User --> UC4
User --> UC5

' Relationships
UC3 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
UC4 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
UC5 ..> UC2 : <<include>>

note right of UC1
  Create for day/week/month
  Add dishes to meals:
  Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner, Snacks
  Select from search
  Customize portions
  Menu templates
  Create from favorites
  AI meal suggestions by goal
end note

note right of UC2
  View in calendar format
  Day/Week/Month views
  Drag & drop to move dishes
  Quick actions: switch meal, delete, copy
  Filter by meal/category/difficulty
end note

note right of UC3
  Drag & drop between meals/days
  Replace, add, remove dishes
  Adjust portions
  Batch edit
  Undo/Redo
  Auto-save drafts
end note

note right of UC5
  **MEDIUM PRIORITY**
  Aggregate ingredients from all recipes
  Merge duplicates
  Convert to standard units
  Multiply by portions
  Subtract Virtual Fridge items
  Group by category
  Smart shopping list
end note

note bottom of UC5
  Integration with UC5 (Virtual Fridge)
  Cross-module data flow
end note

@enduml




